  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">One Village Transformed (OVT) Nkopon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This OVT project aims to build the capacity of the community and bring about lasting transformational development. The project will create sustainable and resilient holistic development in the target community. 

To establish a firm foundation for long-term transformational work in the target villages, World Concern will focus on diversifying livelihoods with the community members through economic empowerment/starting savings and loan groups (ASCAs).  

The project will also work closely with the community and authorities to improve the sanitation and hygiene status.</narrative>
  </description>
